Bugfixes for existing MCS51 peephole rules in peeph.def.

CRITICAL: rule 131 - subb a,#0x01 replaced by dec without carry guard
HIGH:     rule 265 - cpl c / mov bit,c loses carry
HIGH:     rule 247.h - @r%4 typo, should be @r%5 (dead rule)
HIGH:     rule 167 - cpl bit removes mov c,bit side effect
MEDIUM:   rule 143.a - rlc->rl loses carry
MEDIUM:   rule 143.b - rrc->rr loses carry (+ typo in comment)
MEDIUM:   rule 174.a - subb-based dec clobbers A and C
MEDIUM:   rule 174.b - inc clobbers neither A nor C but original does
LOW:      rule 113.a - cjne clobbers C, setb clobbers A
LOW:      rule 253.b - djnz clobbers A (was mov a,%1 / dec a)
LOW:      rule 264 - cjne clobbers A
LOW:      rule 271 - ternary rewrite clobbers A

